Jeff Perry (American actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeff_Perry_(American_actor) 0 Jeffrey Perry (born August 16, 1955) is an American actor of stage, television, and film. He starred in the ABC political drama Scandal from 2012 to 2018. Jeffrey_Perry ( born August_16_,_1955 ) is an_American_actor of stage_,_television , and film .
